word_mean_info__list.difference: 普通用词，含义广泛，侧重因某种原因所产生的最终结果，而不是眼前的结果。
指因某种原因直接产生的结果，着重持续稳定与其影响。
普通用词，多指事物经过一系列发展变化所导致的最终结局，而不是某种原因的直接结果。常可与result通用。
多指随某一事件引起的，必然或自然的不良结果，不强调直接的因果关系，而侧重事件发展的逻辑关系。

bilingual.source: They bet on the outcome of the game.
bilingual.target: 他们在比赛结果上打赌。

bilingual.source: The outcome of this game is random.
bilingual.target: 这个游戏的结果是随机的。

bilingual.source: They guessed the outcome of the game.
bilingual.target: 他们猜测了比赛的结果。

bilingual.source: She does not care at all about the outcome.
The outcome of this matter is hard to say.
The judge decides the outcome of the case.
The outcome of the election is uncertain.
bilingual.target: 选举的结果是不确定的。

bilingual.source: The outcome of the election was surprising.

yingyinNormal.en: Aristotle defined tragedy as a terrible outcome arising from a person's fatal flaw. A flaw, that had it been fixed, would have instead led to a wonderful outcome.
yingyinNormal.zh: 亚里士多德将悲剧定义成个人致命缺点带来的可怕结果。当初要是改善了这个缺点，结果就会大大变好。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, somebody else is gonna want to make a bet on the outcome of their bet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在，有其他人想赌他们赌博的结果。

yingyinNormal.en: And then he purposely crippled your ship in enemy space, leading to one inevitable outcome.
yingyinNormal.zh: 然后他故意在敌人的区域弄坏你的战舰，这样就会产生一个无法避免的结果。

yingyinNormal.en: This is obviously not the outcome we wanted. But we will resume the search the moment it is safe to walk through the forest again.
yingyinNormal.zh: 显然这不是我们想要的结果。当能安全进入森林时我们会继续搜索的。

yingyinNormal.en: But killing Trask did not have the outcome she expected. It only persuaded the government of the need for his program.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是，杀死了特斯拉克并未达到她预期的结果，这反而使得政府坚信特斯拉克的计划是有必要的。

yingyinNormal.en: Our business has grown, but we never lost the sight of our customers, focusing on solving their problems, leads to the best outcome for our business.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们的业务不断发展壮大，但是我们从未丢失对于客户第一的理念，我们始终专注于帮助客户解决问题，基于这点，也成就了我们最好的业务结果。

yingyinNormal.en: But if I had to put you through it again for this outcome. I would.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但如果重来一次的话，为了这个结局，我还是会这么做。

yingyinNormal.en: All right. Indiana Jones plays no role in the outcome of the story.
yingyinNormal.zh: 奉陪到底，故事结尾印第安纳琼斯毫无作用。

yingyinNormal.en: And they'll be nothing to stop the Mimics from conquering the rest of the world. Unless you change the outcome. Me?
yingyinNormal.zh: 它们会横扫一切，统治整个地球，除非你阻挡它们。我?

yingyinNormal.en: They're going to be arguing that there's no reason to keep the defendants in jail until the outcome of the forthcoming trial.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在本庭宣判之前，他们反对将被告收监。

yingyinNormal.en: Mr. President, given the potential outcome that the House will affirm articles of impeachment, is this the right time to wade into a Middle Eastern conflict?
yingyinNormal.zh: 总统先生，鉴于众议院可能提出弹劾令，现在插手中东冲突合适吗？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: the way a thing turns out

examination_example.sentence: Consider the person that you're dealing with in advance and what will get you to your desired <highlight>outcome</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 提前考虑你会和什么人打交道，以及达到你预期的结果需要做些什么。

examination_example.sentence: These results suggest that imagining the <highlight>outcome</highlight> of following through on one's curiosity ahead of time can help determine whether it is worth the endeavor.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些结果表明，提前想象好奇心得到满足后的结果，可以帮助确定这件事是否值得努力。

examination_example.sentence: It does not include important factors such as environmental quality or education <highlight>outcomes</highlight> — all things that contribute to a person's sense of well-being.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它不包括环境质量或教育成果等重要因素——这些因素都有助于实现个人幸福感。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>

sense_info_list.en: the way a thing turns out

examination_example.sentence: Pasta does not have an adverse effect on body weigh <highlight>outcomes</highlight> when it is consumed as part of a healthy dietary pattern..
examination_example.sentence_trans: 作为健康饮食模式的一部分，食用意大利面不会对体重产生不利影响。

examination_example.sentence: In order to achieve a successful <highlight>outcome</highlight> or reward, some level of risk is almost always essential.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 要想获得成功的结果或回报，一定程度的风险几乎总是必不可少的。

examination_example.sentence: Since a change in the course of action can sometimes be important and lead to a positive <highlight>outcome</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因为行动过程中的改变有时是重要的，能带来积极的结果。

数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: the way a thing turns out

examination_example.sentence: There are a lot of studies on the relationship between breakfast eating and possible health <highlight>outcomes</highlight>, but this may be because those who eat breakfast choose to habitually have health-enhancing behaviours such as regular exercise and not smoking.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 关于吃早餐与可能的健康结果之间的关联，有很多研究，但这可能是因为那些吃早餐的人通常会选择有益健康的习惯和行为，比如不抽烟、经常做运动。

examination_example.sentence: For women, delayed marriage — which is related, in part, to labor market <highlight>outcomes</highlight> for men — may explain more of the increase in their living in the family home.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 对于女性来说，推迟结婚——在一定程度上与男性在劳动力市场上就业情形有关——可能更能解释为什么越来越多的女性住在父母家。

examination_example.sentence: He said people will be the winner, whatever the <highlight>outcome</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他说，无论结果如何，人都是赢家。

examination_example.sentence: It is easier to avoid a discussion, but risking talking about it may eventually lead to a better <highlight>outcome</highlight>.

examination_example.sentence: Having confidence in yourself will help you make better choices because you can see what the best <highlight>outcome</highlight> would be for your well-being.
